INTERACTION SPECIFICATIONS

Buttons

Hover State
• Increase shadow.

Pressed State
• Reduce opacity to 90%.

Disabled State
• Gray background with reduced opacity.

Input Fields

Focus State
• Purple border (#7C6CF3).

Error State
• Red border (#EF4444).

Cards

Hover State
• Elevation increases.

Transitions

Duration
• 200ms–300ms

Animation
• Ease In-Out

Progress Bars

